paragraphs.title: shipped NM per shipped Subo - NMSO
paragraphs.text:
run("
SELECT date_add('2022-11-01',cast(datediff(at.orderDate,'2022-11-01')/15 as int)*15) AS date
        ,MIN(at.orderDate) AS startDate
        ,MAX(at.orderDate) AS endDate
        
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%fb%' THEN at.subOrderId ELSE NULL END) / (DATEDIFF(MAX(at.orderDate),MIN(at.orderDate)) + 1) AS avgFBBkdSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%fb%' THEN ftu.orderId ELSE NULL END)/ (DATEDIFF(MAX(at.orderDate),MIN(at.orderDate)) + 1) AS avgFBFTUS
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%fb%' AND (shippedStatus <> 'CLD' OR shippedStatus IS NULL OR shippedStatus='NA') THEN at.subOrderId ELSE NULL END)
            / (DATEDIFF(MAX(at.orderDate),MIN(at.orderDate)) + 1) AS avgFBShpSubo
        ,SUM(CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%fb%' AND (shippedStatus <> 'CLD' OR shippedStatus IS NULL OR shippedStatus='NA') THEN NMIncAd ELSE 0 END)
            / (DATEDIFF(MAX(at.orderDate),MIN(at.orderDate)) + 1) AS avgFBShpNM
        ,SUM(CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%fb%' AND (shippedStatus <> 'CLD' OR shippedStatus IS NULL OR shippedStatus='NA') THEN NMIncAd ELSE 0 END) 
            / COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%fb%' AND (shippedStatus <> 'CLD' OR shippedStatus IS NULL OR shippedStatus='NA') THEN at.subOrderId ELSE NULL END) AS fbNMSO
        
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' THEN at.subOrderId ELSE NULL END) / (DATEDIFF(MAX(at.orderDate),MIN(at.orderDate)) + 1) AS avgGoogleBkdSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' THEN ftu.orderId ELSE NULL END) / (DATEDIFF(MAX(at.orderDate),MIN(at.orderDate)) + 1) AS avgGoogleFTUS
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND (shippedStatus <> 'CLD' OR shippedStatus IS NULL OR shippedStatus='NA') THEN at.subOrderId ELSE NULL END)
            / (DATEDIFF(MAX(at.orderDate),MIN(at.orderDate)) + 1) AS avgGoogleShpSubo
        ,SUM(CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND (shippedStatus <> 'CLD' OR shippedStatus IS NULL OR shippedStatus='NA') THEN NMIncAd ELSE 0 END)
            / (DATEDIFF(MAX(at.orderDate),MIN(at.orderDate)) + 1) AS avgGoogleShpNM
        ,SUM(CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND (shippedStatus <> 'CLD' OR shippedStatus IS NULL OR shippedStatus='NA') THEN NMIncAd ELSE 0 END) 
            / COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND (shippedStatus <> 'CLD' OR shippedStatus IS NULL OR shippedStatus='NA') THEN at.subOrderId ELSE NULL END) AS googleNMSO
FROM(
    SELECT *
    FROM `temp.attributedOrders`
    WHERE orderDate >= '2022-11-01') at

LEFT JOIN(
        SELECT DISTINCT subOrderId
                        ,shippedStatus
        FROM `all(agCmDump)`
        ) ag
ON at.subOrderId = ag.subOrderId

LEFT JOIN `temp.ftus_jatin` ftu
ON ftu.orderId = at.orderId

LEFT JOIN(
        SELECT DISTINCT FROM_UNIXTIME(timestamp/1000) AS orderDate
                        ,NMIncAd 
                        ,subOrderId
        FROM `all(unitEconomicsBaseTable)`
        ) ue
ON at.subOrderId = ue.subOrderId

GROUP BY date_add('2022-11-01',cast(datediff(at.orderDate,'2022-11-01')/15 as int)*15)
",1000)

paragraphs.title: Subo_weekWiseBAU
paragraphs.text:
run("
SELECT date_add('2022-01-02',cast(datediff(orderDate,'2022-01-02')/7 as int)*7) AS week_start_date,deviceType
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT subOrderId)/(DATEDIFF(MAX(orderDate),MIN(orderDate)) + 1) AS avgSDSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%direct%' THEN subOrderId ELSE NULL END)/(DATEDIFF(MAX(orderDate),MIN(orderDate)) + 1) AS avgDirectSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' THEN subOrderId ELSE NULL END)/(DATEDIFF(MAX(orderDate),MIN(orderDate)) + 1) AS avgGoogleSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%pmax%' THEN subOrderId ELSE NULL END)/(DATEDIFF(MAX(orderDate),MIN(orderDate)) + 1) AS avgGooglePMAXSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%ssc%' THEN subOrderId ELSE NULL END)/(DATEDIFF(MAX(orderDate),MIN(orderDate)) + 1) AS avgGoogleSSCSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%discovery%' THEN subOrderId ELSE NULL END)/(DATEDIFF(MAX(orderDate),MIN(orderDate)) + 1) AS avgGoogleDiscoverySubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%yt%' THEN subOrderId ELSE NULL END)/(DATEDIFF(MAX(orderDate),MIN(orderDate)) + 1) AS avgGoogleYtSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND (LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%pmax%' 
                                                                    AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%ssc%' 
                                                                    AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%discovery%'
                                                                    AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%yt%') THEN subOrderId ELSE NULL END)
            /(DATEDIFF(MAX(orderDate),MIN(orderDate)) + 1) AS avgGoogleOtherSubo
        
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%facebook%' THEN subOrderId ELSE NULL END)/(DATEDIFF(MAX(orderDate),MIN(orderDate)) + 1) AS avgFBSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%facebook%' AND LOWER(utmContent) LIKE '%d1%' THEN subOrderId ELSE NULL END)
            /(DATEDIFF(MAX(orderDate),MIN(orderDate)) + 1) AS avgFBD1vSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%facebook%' AND LOWER(utmContent) NOT LIKE '%d1%' THEN subOrderId ELSE NULL END)
            /(DATEDIFF(MAX(orderDate),MIN(orderDate)) + 1) AS avgFBOtherSubo
        
FROM(
    SELECT DISTINCT Channel
                    ,utmContent
                    ,utmCampaign
                    ,subOrderId
                    ,orderDate
                    ,deviceType
    FROM `temp.attributedOrders`
    WHERE orderDate >= '2022-11-01'
    ) ord
JOIN(
    SELECT DISTINCT TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(timestamp/1000)) AS date 
                    ,dayType 
    FROM `last100Days(saleDayMappingMaster)` 
    WHERE dayType = 'BAU'
    ) dt
ON ord.orderDate = dt.date

GROUP BY date_add('2022-01-02',cast(datediff(orderDate,'2022-01-02')/7 as int)*7),deviceType
ORDER BY week_start_date ASC
",1000)

                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%discovery%' THEN 'Discovery_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%yt_trueview_menfashion_influencer_roas_7d_rtu_230123%' THEN 'Yt_Camp_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%yt%' 
                                                    AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%yt_trueview_menfashion_influencer_roas_7d_rtu_230123%' THEN 'Yt_Others_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%yt%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%discovery%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%ssc%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%pmax%' THEN 'Others_Google'
                ELSE 'Others' END AS Channel
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT v.orderId) AS orders
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT v.guid) AS users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT d.guid) AS ftus
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) = 0) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D0_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) = 1) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D1_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) BETWEEN 2 AND 5) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D2to5_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) BETWEEN 6 AND 10) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D6to10_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) BETWEEN 11 AND 15) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D11to15_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) > 15) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D15plus_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN prevVstDate IS NULL AND prevVstSessionId IS NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS NoVisitAfter_1Oct_Users
FROM(
    SELECT *
            ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY guid,orderId ORDER BY date_diff ASC) AS rank
    FROM `temp.ord_PrevVisit`
    ) v

JOIN(
    SELECT DISTINCT TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(timestamp/1000)) AS date 
                    ,dayType 
    FROM `last100Days(saleDayMappingMaster)` 
    WHERE dayType = 'BAU'
    ) dt
ON v.orderDate = dt.date
   
LEFT JOIN `temp.ftusData` d
ON v.orderId = d.orderId AND rank = 1

WHERE rank = 1

GROUP BY date_add('2022-01-02',cast(datediff(orderDate,'2022-01-02')/7 as int)*7)
        ,deviceType
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%pmax%' THEN 'PMAX_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%ssc%' THEN 'SSC_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%discovery%' THEN 'Discovery_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%yt_trueview_menfashion_influencer_roas_7d_rtu_230123%' THEN 'Yt_Camp_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%yt%' 
                                                    AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%yt_trueview_menfashion_influencer_roas_7d_rtu_230123%' THEN 'Yt_Others_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%yt%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%discovery%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%ssc%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%pmax%' THEN 'Others_Google'
                ELSE 'Others' END

ORDER BY week_start_date DESC
",1000)

            WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%discovery%' THEN 'Discovery_Google'

                                                    AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%discovery%'
                                                    AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%ssc%'
                                                    AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%pmax%' THEN 'Others_Google'
                ELSE 'Others' END) AS Channel

        ,COUNT(DISTINCT v.guid) AS users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT d.guid) AS ftus
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) = 0)

        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) = 1)

        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) BETWEEN 11 AND 15)

        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) > 15) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D15plus_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN prevVstDate IS NULL AND prevVstSessionId IS NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS NoVisitAfter_1Oct_Users
FROM(
    SELECT *
            ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY guid,orderId ORDER BY date_diff ASC) AS rank
    FROM `temp.ord_PrevVisit_noVisitAttrib`

ON v.orderId = d.orderId AND rank = 1

paragraphs.text:
run("
SELECT orderDate
        ,deviceType
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%pmax%' THEN 'PMAX_Google'
                
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%ssc%' THEN 'SSC_Google'
                
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%discovery_firebase_maxc_7d_rtu%' THEN 'Discovery_Camp_Google'
                
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%discovery%'
                                                    AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%discovery_firebase_maxc_7d_rtu%' THEN 'Discovery_Others_Google'
                
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%yt_trueview_menfashion_influencer_roas_7d_rtu_230123%' THEN 'Yt_Camp_Google'
                
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%yt%' 
                                                    AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%yt_trueview_menfashion_influencer_roas_7d_rtu_230123%' THEN 'Yt_Others_Google'
                
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%yt%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%discovery%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%ssc%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%pmax%' THEN 'Others_Google'
                ELSE 'Others' END AS Channel
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT v.orderId) AS orders
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT v.guid) AS users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT d.guid) AS ftus
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) = 0) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D0_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) = 1) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D1_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) BETWEEN 2 AND 5) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D2to5_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) BETWEEN 6 AND 10) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D6to10_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) BETWEEN 11 AND 15) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D11to15_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (DATEDIFF(orderDate,prevVstDate) > 15) 
                                                        AND prevVstSessionId IS NOT NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS D15plus_LastVisit_Users
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN prevVstDate IS NULL AND prevVstSessionId IS NULL THEN v.guid ELSE NULL END) AS NoVisitAfter_1Oct_Users
FROM(
    SELECT *
            ,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY guid,orderId ORDER BY date_diff ASC) AS rank
    FROM `temp.ord_PrevVisit`
    ) v
   
LEFT JOIN `temp.ftusData` d
ON v.orderId = d.orderId AND rank = 1

WHERE rank = 1

GROUP BY orderDate
        ,deviceType
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%pmax%' THEN 'PMAX_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%ssc%' THEN 'SSC_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%discovery_firebase_maxc_7d_rtu%' THEN 'Discovery_Camp_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%discovery%'
                                                    AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%discovery_firebase_maxc_7d_rtu%' THEN 'Discovery_Others_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%yt_trueview_menfashion_influencer_roas_7d_rtu_230123%' THEN 'Yt_Camp_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) LIKE '%yt%' 
                                                    AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%yt_trueview_menfashion_influencer_roas_7d_rtu_230123%' THEN 'Yt_Others_Google'
                WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%google%' AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%yt%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%discovery%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%ssc%'
                                                        AND LOWER(utmCampaign) NOT LIKE '%pmax%' THEN 'Others_Google'
                ELSE 'Others' END

ORDER BY orderDate DESC
",1000)
